      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S ALL FIRE (1) jumps from box 1 for the first time after scoring at Q Parklands (29.51) in a Grade 5. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Looks to have an edge on most of these. NON STOP WHISKEY (2) was a winner two back and strongly fancied last time but could only manage fourth (25.83) at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Worth following up. GIVE ME BUCKS (7) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from six starts. Recorded a 4 length win (25.40) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. MAN ON FIRE (4) is always a threat when he races at this journey.",
